---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import SidePanel from '../../../components/SidePanel.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Storehaus RTS Terms of Service | Team Respawn"
  description="Terms of Service for the Storehaus RTS Discord Bot. Learn the rules, acceptable use, and service limitations."
  keywords="Storehaus RTS, terms of service, Discord bot, acceptable use"
  canonical="https://www.teamrespawn.net/storehaus/terms-of-service"
  ogTitle="Storehaus RTS Terms of Service | Team Respawn"
  ogDescription="Terms of Service for the Storehaus RTS Discord Bot. Learn the rules, acceptable use, and service limitations."
  ogImage="https://www.teamrespawn.net/content/Team-Respawn-Full.png"
>
  <a
    href="#main-content"
    class="sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:absolute focus:top-4 focus:left-4 focus:z-50 focus:bg-white focus:text-black focus:px-4 focus:py-2 focus:rounded"
  >
    Skip to main content
  </a>

  <div class="container mx-auto p-4 sm:p-8">
    <Header />

    <main id="main-content" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8" role="main" aria-label="Terms of Service content">
      <article class="bg-gray-800/60 border border-gray-700/60 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10">
        <header class="mb-8">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400">
            Terms of Service
          </h1>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
            <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2026
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Introduction</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the Storehaus RTS Discord Bot ("the Bot", "we", "us", or "our"). By using the Bot, you agree to follow these Terms.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Eligibility</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              You must comply with Discord's Terms of Service and be at least 13 years old to use the Bot. If you are under the age required by your local law to use Discord, do not use the Bot.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Service Description</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The Bot provides game statistics, strategy information, and AI-assisted responses for RTS titles. Features may change, improve, or be discontinued at any time without notice.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Acceptable Use</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              You agree to use the Bot responsibly and to not:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-2 text-gray-300 ml-4">
              <li>Abuse, spam, or overload the Bot with excessive requests</li>
              <li>Attempt to bypass rate limits or access restricted functionality</li>
              <li>Use the Bot for unlawful, harmful, or deceptive activities</li>
              <li>Reverse engineer, scrape, or misuse Bot responses or data</li>
              <li>Impersonate others or misrepresent your affiliation with the Bot</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Data and Content</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The Bot may process command inputs to deliver responses. You are responsible for the content you submit through commands. Do not submit sensitive or private information.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The Bot relies on third-party services (such as Discord and game data providers). Your use of those services is subject to their own terms and policies.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Availability and Changes</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The Bot is provided on an "as-is" and "as-available" basis. We may update, suspend, or discontinue the Bot at any time for any reason.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Disclaimer</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The Bot's responses are provided for informational purposes and may be incomplete or inaccurate. Use the information at your own risk.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              To the maximum extent permitted by law, we are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Bot.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Termination</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We may restrict or terminate access to the Bot for violations of these Terms or for any other reason, with or without notice.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Changes to These Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We may update these Terms from time to time. The "Last Updated" date indicates when changes were made. Continued use of the Bot after changes means you accept the updated Terms.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Contact</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              If you have questions about these Terms, contact the Bot operator through the Discord server where the Bot is hosted.
            </p>
          </section>

          <footer class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-700">
            <p class="text-gray-400 italic">
              <strong>Note:</strong> This Bot is operated independently and is not affiliated with Microsoft, 343 Industries, Relic Entertainment, or any game publishers. All game data and statistics are provided for informational purposes only.
            </p>
          </footer>
        </div>
      </article>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </div>

  <SidePanel />

  <script src="/js/side-panel.js" is:inline></script>
  <script src="/js/tabs.js" is:inline></script>
  <script src="/js/dropdowns.js" is:inline></script>
  <script src="/js/secondary-init.js" is:inline></script>
</BaseLayout>
